00:02:35.850 --> 00:02:37.350
Formulas plus tricks.

00:02:37.769 --> 00:02:42.959
All right, let's get to the magic spells,
the formulas and tricks for finding

00:02:42.959 --> 00:02:46.920
the total number of persons when you
know one person's rank from both sides.

00:02:47.070 --> 00:02:48.299
Just remember this.

00:02:48.720 --> 00:02:53.340
Total equals rank from left,
plus rank from right minus one.

00:02:53.670 --> 00:02:54.720
Why minus one?

00:02:54.870 --> 00:02:57.299
Because you counted the poor fellow twice.

00:02:57.510 --> 00:02:57.990
Simple, right.

00:02:58.830 --> 00:03:02.130
To find the rank from the
other end, you just do total

00:03:02.250 --> 00:03:04.530
minus the known rank plus one.

00:03:04.890 --> 00:03:08.100
It is like looking at the
entire line from the other side.

00:03:08.579 --> 00:03:13.110
Now, finding the number of persons
between two persons has two scenarios.

00:03:13.500 --> 00:03:17.220
If it's a non-overlapping case,
meaning the total is greater than

00:03:17.220 --> 00:03:21.060
the sum of their ranks, the number
of people between them is simply the

00:03:21.060 --> 00:03:22.980
total minus the sum of their ranks.

00:03:23.470 --> 00:03:27.730
But if it's an overlapping case where
the sum of the ranks is more than the

00:03:27.730 --> 00:03:30.040
total, the formula is a bit tricky.

00:03:30.429 --> 00:03:33.970
It's the sum of their ranks
minus the total, and then

00:03:33.970 --> 00:03:35.739
you must subtract two more.

00:03:36.070 --> 00:03:40.600
These two are the people themselves
and for interchanging positions,

00:03:40.719 --> 00:03:44.829
the total is the new position of the
first person, plus the old position

00:03:44.829 --> 00:03:47.019
of the second person minus one.

00:03:47.410 --> 00:03:50.410
The number of people between
them is just the difference in

00:03:50.410 --> 00:03:52.899
positions of one person minus one.

00:03:53.250 --> 00:03:53.760
Got it.

00:03:54.000 --> 00:03:54.450
Good.

