00:04:02.055 --> 00:04:07.065
So here is the step-by-step method for
calculating photo persons in a row.

00:04:07.155 --> 00:04:11.685
First hunt down that one person whose
rank is given from both left and right.

00:04:12.225 --> 00:04:16.635
Add those two ranks, and please
