opposite ends is less than the

00:04:40.445 --> 00:04:44.585
total, it's non-overlapping,
if it's more, it's overlapping.

00:04:44.915 --> 00:04:48.875
For the non-overlapping case, subtract
the sum of the ranks from the total

00:04:49.205 --> 00:04:53.300
for the overlapping case, subtract the
total, and two from the sum of the ranks.

00:04:53.985 --> 00:04:56.685
Easy peasy for interchanging positions.

