00:11:30.945 --> 00:11:35.055
P is 12th from the left end, and
Q is 18th from the right end.

00:11:35.355 --> 00:11:44.325
How many friends are sitting between P
and Q options A 19 B, 20 C, 20 1D 22?

00:11:44.685 --> 00:11:47.595
Understand the question
before moving to explanation.

00:11:48.980 --> 00:11:51.380
Step one, let's list what we know.

00:11:51.710 --> 00:11:56.990
Total friends equals 50 peace
position from left equals 12 Q's

00:11:56.990 --> 00:11:59.120
position from right equals 18th.

00:11:59.480 --> 00:12:02.180
Step two, let's check for overlapping.

00:12:02.449 --> 00:12:06.620
Some of positions equals
12 plus 18, which is 30.

00:12:06.920 --> 00:12:10.670
Since the total 50 is
greater than the sum 30.

00:12:10.790 --> 00:12:12.829
This is a non-overlapping case.

00:12:13.010 --> 00:12:13.880
They don't cross each other.

00:12:14.710 --> 00:12:15.490
Step three.

00:12:15.790 --> 00:12:19.930
Now we apply the simple formula
for non-overlapping cases, which

00:12:19.930 --> 00:12:25.510
is persons between equals total
minus sum of ranks, so persons

00:12:25.510 --> 00:12:29.440
between equals 50 minus 12 plus 18.

00:12:29.710 --> 00:12:33.430
That becomes 50 minus 30, which equals 20.

00:12:33.670 --> 00:12:39.400
Therefore there are 20 friends sitting
between P and Q. Correct answer B 20.

